topPRs.body:
**We need to merge this first:** https://github.com/elizaOS/eliza/pull/6212

* **New Features**
  * Added streaming text generation support for enhanced real-time output.
  * Added comprehensive test coverage for plugin functionality.

* **Chores**
  * Bumped package version to 1.5.16.
  * Updated @elizaos/core dependency to ^1.6.5.

* **Refactor**
  * Streamlined text generation handlers for improved efficiency.
  * Enhanced schema handling for object generation operations.
  * Removed tool integration features from text generation models.
